sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant HTTP as HTTP Server (FastAPI)<br/>8080/TCP
    participant GRPC as gRPC Server<br/>8085/TCP
    participant PW as PydanticWrapper
    participant GPS as GlobalPredictServicer
    participant MM as ModelManager
    participant Module as Module.run()
    participant MMesh as Model Mesh Controller
    participant MRS as ModelRuntimeServicer
    participant CML as CoreModelLoader
    participant HP as caikit_health_probe
    participant K8s as Kubernetes kubelet

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,Module: Flow 1: HTTP Model Inference
        Client->>HTTP: POST /api/v1/tasks/{task}/predict<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (Configurable TLS/mTLS)
        HTTP->>PW: Route to handler<br/>Request validation (Pydantic)
        PW->>GPS: Validated request<br/>(DataBase objects)
        GPS->>MM: Fetch loaded model<br/>(model_id lookup)
        MM-->>GPS: LoadedModel reference
        GPS->>Module: Module.run(request)<br/>(in-process inference)
        Module-->>GPS: Prediction result
        GPS-->>PW: Response (DataBase)
        PW-->>HTTP: JSON or SSE stream
        HTTP-->>Client: 200 OK<br/>JSON response or SSE stream
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Client,Module: Flow 2: gRPC Model Inference
        Client->>GRPC: InferenceService.Predict()<br/>gRPC (Configurable TLS/mTLS)
        GRPC->>GPS: CaikitRuntimeServerWrapper<br/>intercepts & routes
        GPS->>MM: Fetch loaded model<br/>(model_id lookup)
        MM-->>GPS: LoadedModel reference
        GPS->>Module: Module.run(request)<br/>(in-process inference)
        Module-->>GPS: Prediction result
        GPS-->>GRPC: Proto message or server stream
        GRPC-->>Client: gRPC response
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over MMesh,CML: Flow 3: Model Mesh Integration
        MMesh->>MRS: loadModel(model_id, path)<br/>Unix socket /tmp/mmesh/grpc.sock<br/>gRPC (no encryption)
        MRS->>MM: ModelManager.load_model()
        MM->>CML: CoreModelLoader.load()
        CML->>CML: caikit.core.load(model_path)
        CML-->>MM: Loaded model instance
        MM-->>MRS: Load success + model size
        MRS-->>MMesh: LoadModelResponse

        MMesh->>MRS: modelSize(model_id)<br/>Unix socket
        MRS-->>MMesh: ModelSizeResponse

        MMesh->>MRS: unloadModel(model_id)<br/>Unix socket
        MRS->>MM: ModelManager.unload_model()
        MM-->>MRS: Unload success
        MRS-->>MMesh: UnloadModelResponse
    end

    rect rgb(252, 228, 236)
        Note over K8s,GRPC: Flow 4: Health Probe
        K8s->>HP: Exec liveness probe<br/>(process check via psutil)
        HP->>HTTP: GET /health<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (matches server config)
        HTTP-->>HP: 200 OK
        HP->>GRPC: grpc.health.v1.Health.Check()<br/>gRPC (matches server config)
        GRPC-->>HP: SERVING
        HP-->>K8s: Exit code 0 (healthy)
    end
